   Marketing &amp; Media -- Advertising:
   Hotels Promote Cheaper Rates,
   But the Strategy Has Some Risks
   ----
   By Jonathan Dahl
</HL>
<DATE>
09/19/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B11
